==German==
===Etymology===
From ''[[Schmetten]]'' "cream", compare [[butterfly]]. Also "Schmettern", the movement one makes when taking something up and throwing it down. 
===Noun===
'''Schmetterling''' ''m'' (''pl'' Schmetterlinge)
# [[butterfly]] (insect)
# [[butterfly]] (swimming stroke)

